Hello, <%= @customer.name %>

You have successfully booked a flight!

Below is your flight information:

Flight #: <%= @booking.flight_id %>
From: <%= @booking.flight.from_airport.airport_code %>
To: <%= @booking.flight.to_airport.airport_code %>
Date: <%= @booking.flight.start_time.strftime("%a %b %d, %Y") %>
Time: <%= @booking.flight.start_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %>

<% @booking.passengers.each_with_index do |p, i| %>
    Passenger <%= i + 1 %>:
    Name: <%= p.name %>
    Email: <%= p.email %>
<% end %>